The gzip'ed tar file contains source code, tests, and documentation
for the package for computing Hilbert bases of linear Diophantine 
equations,  implementing the algorithm described in my paper 
"Computing the Hilbert base via the Elliott-MacMahon algorithm", Th. Computer Science 263 (2001) 37-46

Copyright (C) 1996-2001, 2005	Dmitrii V. Pasechnik
			Tilburg University, The Netherlands.
			e-mail: dimpase@gmail.com

This program is free software.  You can redistribute it and/or modify it under
the terms of the GNU General Public License as published by the Free Software
