version. For details, see the file COPYING in the current directory, or
see The FSF's own site.

----------------------------------------------------------

do make and then, say 
main.exe <Tests/hppi4
if you want to find Hilbert base of
the system in the file Tests/hppi4

the format is as follows:

prtlevel #of_equations #of_variables
equation_1
equation_2
...

The output is written in the file base
in the same directory
